snippet.title: ☆ Find Arc Length and Sector Area of a Circle  | Common Core Geometry
snippet.description:
Join us on this flipped math lesson where we visually explore the arc length and sector area of a circle. For more MashUp Math content, visit http://www.mashupmath.com and join our free mailing list! :)

This lesson answers the questions: How do I find arc length? How do I find sector area? How do I find a missing arc? What is a central angle? What is theta? How do I find the area of a shaded region?

Our lessons are perfect for flipped classroom math teachers and students. This lesson is aligned with the common core learning standards for math and the SAT math curriculum as well.

Be sure to join our mailing list at http://www.mashupmath.com
